# Import Process

Step 1 – Upload Source File

A CSV file containing employee information is uploaded into ServiceNow.

Step 2 – Import Set Creation

The uploaded file populates the Import Set table.

Table name:
u_employee_import

Step 3 – Data Staging

Data remains in the staging table until a Transform Map processes it.

Step 4 – Transform Execution

The Transform Map converts source data into structured employee records.
